dct_title_s: A mar [sic] of part of Borneo and the Sooloo Archipelago : laid down chiefly from observations made in 1761, 2, 3, and 4
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. "In testimony of respect, gratitude and affection, to the right Honourable George Lord Pigot ... this map engraved at his expence, is inscribed by ... Alexander Dalrymple." In upper right margin: 54.
